Class GUIinterface

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • GUIinterface

  • public class GUIinterface
extends javafx.application.Application
    This class manages/controls the GUIWorld so the user can see the world as well as control it as they require. This class also handles the opening and saving of configuration files.

      • start

        public void start(javafx.stage.Stage primaryStage)
        This function is for displaying the actual control window. The parameter for this class is @param primaryStage. As this function is run when the stage is created, the runtime thread for visualising the entities is also in this function. The menu code is in this function as it needs to be shown on start up.
